---
title: Campaigns at Leeds Night Owls
description: "Campaigns are a series of linked wargames run by Leeds Night Owls."
layout: page
eleventyNavigation:
  key: Campaigns
  order: 6
breadcrumbs:
  - title: Home
    url: /
breadcrumbLabel: Campaigns
---

{% set currentCampaigns = [] %}
{% set pastCampaigns = [] %}
{% for campaign in collections.campaigns %}
  {% if campaign.data.activeCampaign %}
    {% set currentCampaigns = (currentCampaigns.push(campaign), currentCampaigns) %}
  {% else %}
    {% set pastCampaigns = (pastCampaigns.push(campaign), pastCampaigns) %}
  {% endif %}
{% endfor %}

<h1>Campaigns at Leeds Night Owls</h1>
<p>Leeds Night Owls runs a number of campaigns, from the American Civil War to the Second World War and beyond.</p>

<h2 class="mt-4">Active Campaigns</h2>

{% if currentCampaigns.length == 0 %}
<p class="text-muted">There are no active campaigns active at the moment. Check back soon, or <a href="/contact-us/">get in touch</a> to find out what's being planned.</p>
{% else %}
  {% for campaign in currentCampaigns %}
  <div class="row mb-4 border-bottom pb-4">
    {% if campaign.data.thumbnail %}
    <div class="col-md-4">
      <a href="{{ campaign.url }}">
        <img src="{{ campaign.data.thumbnail }}" alt="{{ campaign.data.thumbnailAlt }}" class="img-fluid rounded" style="max-height: 220px; width: 100%; object-fit: cover;">
      </a>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-8">
    {% else %}
    <div class="col-12">
    {% endif %}
      <h3><a href="{{ campaign.url }}" class="text-decoration-none">{{ campaign.data.title }}</a></h3>
      {% if campaign.data.description %}<p>{{ campaign.data.description }}</p>{% endif %}
      <a href="{{ campaign.url }}" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm">View campaign</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  {% endfor %}
{% endif %}

<h2 class="mt-4">Past Campaigns</h2>

{% if pastCampaigns.length == 0 %}
<p class="text-muted">No past campaigns recorded.</p>
{% else %}
  {% for campaign in pastCampaigns | sort(true, false, "data.campaignDate") %}
  <div class="row mb-4 border-bottom pb-4">
    {% if campaign.data.thumbnail %}
    <div class="col-md-4">
      <a href="{{ campaign.url }}">
        <img src="{{ campaign.data.thumbnail }}" alt="{{ campaign.data.thumbnailAlt }}" class="img-fluid rounded" style="max-height: 220px; width: 100%; object-fit: cover;">
      </a>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-8">
    {% else %}
    <div class="col-12">
    {% endif %}
      <h3><a href="{{ campaign.url }}" class="text-decoration-none">{{ campaign.data.title }}</a></h3>
      <p class="text-muted">{{ campaign.data.campaignDate | readableDate }}</p>
      {% if campaign.data.description %}<p>{{ campaign.data.description }}</p>{% endif %}
      <a href="{{ campaign.url }}" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm">View campaign</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  {% endfor %}
{% endif %}
